reviewText: Another great small group study by Chip.  We have been using this one in our Sunday School Class and are always excited to dig deeper into his studies.  Highly recommend this study.  God Bless.
DVD was damaged upon receipt but materials were excellent

We think we know how to manage our time until we find ourselves completely overwhelmed.  This simple tool (think screwdriver, simple but extremely effective) is encouraging, not condemning.  This is not another checklist to accomplish but guidance to help dig ourselves out of the deep hole of feeling like we have to do everything all the time.
We have just begun watching this series the first two sessions have been very challenging and helpful. I would reccomend this series especially for young adults.
